2
00:00:08,320 --> 00:00:09,820
[Nam Siwoo... 
Ide mu basketbal! Budeme mu fandiť!]

3
00:00:10,570 --> 00:00:12,400
[EP. 23 Basketbal sa ráta]

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:17,150
- Prečo je sama?
- Pohádala sa s Do Hanou.

5
00:00:17,150 --> 00:00:19,000
Nevidela si to?

6
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,430
- Bola neuveriteľná.
- Je pravé meno je Kim Joyeon.

7
00:00:22,550 --> 00:00:24,760
Prečo si ho zmenila?

8
00:00:24,950 --> 00:00:25,760
Nevieš?

9
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:29,880
Rodičia niekedy menia meno dieťaťa, 
lebo im to radí veštec.

10
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:31,270
Veštec?

11
00:00:31,510 --> 00:00:35,520
Kim Hana, vraj pôjdeš von s Boram.

12
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:39,880
Čo? Áno, aj s Hanou.

13
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,860
Čo je to?

14
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:45,220
Doha mi to dala.

15
00:00:45,490 --> 00:00:46,790
Doha?

16
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:52,110
Čo to bolo?

17
00:00:52,680 --> 00:00:55,180
Neporušuješ tým pravidlá, 
keď spolu nechodíte?

18
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:58,080
- Neporušujeme, lebo spolu nechodíme.
- Keďže s ňou nechodíš...

19
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,740
Si Sokrates, či čo?

20
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:04,660
Mätie ma to. Nebuď arogantný.

21
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:07,400
Poďme si pozrieť Siwooovu hru.
Do Hana na vás čaká.

22
00:01:07,710 --> 00:01:08,700
Poďme.

23
00:01:23,450 --> 00:01:26,820
- Nam Siwoo je úžasný!
- Úžasnejší, než ja?

24
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:30,420
Siwoo sa snaží. Škoda, že sa snaží ako jediný.

25
00:01:31,010 --> 00:01:34,210
Siwoo hrá lepšie, než ostatní, však?

26
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:46,460
Toto by sa malo rátať tiež.

27
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:49,140
- Mám chuť na KFC.
- Prečo by to mali rátať?

28
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:51,770
Ak spraví protihráč faul, kým druhý hádže,

29
00:01:51,770 --> 00:01:54,750
tak má potom napadnutý hráč právo na voľné hody.

30
00:01:55,490 --> 00:01:58,310
Má teraz dve šance! Snaž sa, Nam Siwoo!

31
00:01:58,310 --> 00:02:00,110
Ideš!

32
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:00,890
- Čo je s ním?
- Prečo to robí?

33
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:02,840
To nie.

34
00:03:13,950 --> 00:03:14,960
Jedna strela!

35
00:03:19,410 --> 00:03:21,210
Nam Siwoo!

36
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:32,310
Musí uspieť!

37
00:03:50,270 --> 00:03:51,910
Hej, Lee Jeongmin.

38
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:55,160
Lee Jeongmin?

39
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,610
Asi prehrám.

40
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:22,120
Takže?

41
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:28,240
Minule si to vravel.

42
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:31,320
Že je sranda aj keď prehráš.

43
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:35,310
Áno.

44
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:40,100
Prehra je výhra.

45
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:42,710
Nie, prehra je prehra.

46
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:45,800
Výhra je výhra.

47
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:53,960
Včera si mi niečo sľúbil.

48
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:56,700
Nedodržíš to?

49
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:06,800
- Čo mi chceš povedať?
- Budeš so mnou chodiť?

50
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:15,360
Priamy útok. Bežím priamo a skórujem.

51
00:05:15,630 --> 00:05:19,110
Vieš, čo je dnes za deň?

52
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:22,530
16. september.

53
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:27,130
Predvečer dňa priznania.

54
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:29,440
Oslavuješ taký deň?

55
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:33,410
Nie, neoslavujem.

56
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,170
Ale...

57
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:38,060
Prečo sa mi nevyznáš zajtra?

58
00:05:39,730 --> 00:05:42,770
Ak spolu začneme chodiť zajtra, 
Vianoce budú naším 100. dňom.

59
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:44,920
Tak...

60
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:51,690
povieš áno, ak ťa pozvem von?

61
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:56,100
Prečo to vnímaš takto?

62
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,500
Len tak.

63
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:08,580
Keď si so mnou dnes začneš, 
Vianoce budú naším 100. dňom.

64
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,860
Takže?

65
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:14,770
Len vravím.

66
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:19,600
Na takých veciach mi nezáleží.

67
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:23,590
Budeš so mnou chodiť?

68
00:06:23,590 --> 00:06:25,140
Odskočenie.

69
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:28,640
Tá otázka sa odrazila od koša.

70
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,340
Chytil som ju a hodil znovu.

71
00:06:33,740 --> 00:06:38,120
Odpoviem ti, keď vyhráš súťaž.

72
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:41,670
Vyhral som.

73
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:43,760
Odskočenie, znovu.

74
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:46,600
Myslím finálový zápas.

75
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,880
Toto je... faulovanie.

76
00:06:53,990 --> 00:06:55,310
Dobre.

77
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:01,700
Sľúb mi to.

78
00:07:07,050 --> 00:07:08,260
Sľubujem.

79
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:18,770
Och...

80
00:07:18,770 --> 00:07:23,050
Tiež mi niečo sľúb.

81
00:07:24,220 --> 00:07:28,660
Toto je faul.

82
00:07:28,660 --> 00:07:30,860
Už som ti sľub dala.

83
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,800
Musíš vymazať tú kresbu v telefóne.

84
00:07:33,820 --> 00:07:36,200
Hneď ju vymažem.

85
00:07:37,380 --> 00:07:38,460
Tak mi sľúb...

86
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:42,960
Ak nastane faul, 
môžem získať voľnú šancu na skórovanie.

87
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,030
Čo?

88
00:07:45,410 --> 00:07:51,140
Ak trafím, ráta sa to ako bod.

89
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:56,160
Ak vyhrám, povedz áno.

90
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,480
Dobre.

91
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,720
Trafil som.

92
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,440
Skóroval som.

93
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:17,720
Hej, čo robíš?

94
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,390
Len...

95
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:23,100
Čo je s tebou?

96
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:25,740
Sľúb to.

97
00:08:38,180 --> 00:08:39,490
Minki! Minki!

98
00:08:46,050 --> 00:08:50,230
Nam Siwoo! Nam Siwoo!
Nam Siwoo! Nam Siwoo!

99
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:51,350
Dobre, dobre!

100
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:53,250
To je Do Hanin efekt?

101
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:54,240
Prečo?

102
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:57,110
Siwoo a Doha sa spolu bavili.

103
00:08:59,450 --> 00:09:02,730
Siwoo zase skóroval! Pozri sa na to!

104
00:09:02,730 --> 00:09:05,690
- Fešák!
- Že? Pristane mu to!

105
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:41,050
Zase skóroval! Zase!

106
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:15,170
Páni, je mužný!

107
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:25,230
Čo? Aký sľub?

108
00:10:25,230 --> 00:10:27,250
Spomínaš si, že?

109
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:29,990
Zabudla som.

110
00:10:29,990 --> 00:10:32,860
Nemôžeš. To by bol faul.

111
00:10:34,470 --> 00:10:38,150
- Au!
- Miláčik! Si v poriadku? Hej!

112
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:40,370
- Hej!
- Vy dvaja!

113
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:44,070
Hej!

114
00:10:52,970 --> 00:10:54,330
Čo?

115
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:05,000
Teraz sa bozkávajú?

